body.body: Speed Triple (from VIN 461332 to VIN 733009) and Speed Triple R (to VIN 733009)

Semi or fully synthetic 10W/40 or 10W/50 engine oil which meets specification API SH (or higher) and JASO MA. Triumph recommends Castrol Power 1 Racing 4T 10W/40 or 10W/50 (fully synthetic) engine oil, sold as Castrol Power RS Racing 4T 10W/40 or 10W/50 (fully synthetic) in some countries
3.2 litres (oil and filter change). Always refer to the dipstick/filler plug markings for correct level
Triumph HD4X Hybrid OAT coolant (premixed as supplied by Triumph)
Lubricate the seals for the camshaft cover bolts with clean engine oil
Tighten the camshaft cover bolts in the sequence shown below. Bolts 1 and 4 are torqued twice, the second time as 7 and 8
Chain spray suitable for O-ring chains
Chain spray suitable for O-ring chains
Must not exceed 1.2A (refer to the service manual)
Showa SS8 (SAE 10W) (Speed Triple), Ã–hlins fork oil (Speed Tripe R)
For current parts information, refer to the Electronic Parts Catalogue.
